---
title: Beef Burrito Night with Refried Beans, Queso Fresco, Peppers, and Onion
description: You’ll be on a roll with these burritos that will make your whole family say “Olé!” There’s no shortage of festive fillings to stuff inside—from creamy refried beans to mildly-spiced beef to soft and sweet onions and peppers, everyone will have their pick of Tex-Mex-style ingredients to choose from. In fact, we heartily suggest that you invite your gang to assemble their own tortillas tableside so that they can make their tubular torpedos of tastiness just the way they like.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/beef-burrito-night-c79ef037.jpg
